    "html": "<DOCUMENT>\n<TYPE>EX-99.1\n<SEQUENCE>2\n<FILENAME>ego_ex991.htm\n<DESCRIPTION>ANNUAL AND SPECIAL MEETING OF SHAREHOLDERS VOTING RESULTS\n<TEXT>\n<html><head><title>ego_ex991.htm</title><!--Document created using EDGARMaster--></head><body style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT: 10pt times new roman\"><p style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; MARGIN: 0px; text-align:right;\"><strong>EXHIBIT 99.1</strong></p> <p style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; MARGIN: 0px; text-align:justify;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; MARGIN: 0px; text-align:right;\"><img src=\"ego_ex991img1.jpg\"></p> <p style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; MARGIN: 0px; text-align:justify;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; MARGIN: 0px; text-align:justify;\"><strong>VIA SEDAR</strong></p> <p style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; MARGIN: 0px; text-align:justify;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; MARGIN: 0px; text-align:justify;\">To the Securities Regulatory Authorities:</p> <p style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; MARGIN: 0px; text-align:justify;\">&nbsp;</p> <table style=\"border-spacing:0;text-align:left;font:10pt times new roman;width:100%\" cellpadding=\"0\"> <tr style=\"height:15px\"> <td style=\"width:4%;\"> <p style=\"margin:0px\"><strong>RE:</strong></p></td> <td style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><strong>Eldorado Gold Corporation (the &#8220;Company&#8221;)</strong></td></tr> <tr style=\"height:15px\"> <td> <p style=\"margin:0px\">&nbsp;</p></td> <td style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><strong>Report of Voting Results pursuant to Section 11.3 of </strong></td></tr> <tr style=\"height:15px\"> <td> <p style=\"margin:0px\">&nbsp;</p></td> <td style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><strong></strong><strong>National Instrument 51-102 Continuous Disclosure Obligations (&#8220;NI-51-102&#8221;)</strong></td></tr></table>&